<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="20Sep1922"><font color="red">20 September 1922</font>, <cite>Letters I</cite> (JJ to Harriet Weaver): I should be glad to know as soon as possible whether the few corrections which we agreed to make of hideous blunders are being made. Perhaps a short note, similar to that in the first edition, could be inserted.</div>
